data.description: Introducing this meticulously maintained and tastefully updated home nestled in a premier location of the highly sought-after Cathedral City Cove. Enter through the front patio gate and be enchanted by the completely tranquil setting featuring pristine desert landscaping, a rock fountain, privacy, and picturesque views of the mountains. Inside the home, you'll notice every room in this house showcases your beautiful outdoor space through various dual pane sliders and expansive windows. The living room is equipped with an aesthetic, stone fireplace. The remodeled kitchen comes equipped with stainless steel appliances, cabinets with custom pull-outs, granite counters, and a stylish backsplash. Fitting in with the trend of this impeccable home, the backyard is very spacious with a sparkling, kidney-shaped pool, beautiful lush landscaping, mountain views, and plenty of patio space for entertaining. The sizable primary bedroom has well-placed windows once again showcasing your lush outdoor space, as well as two closets for all of your wardrobe needs. Both bathrooms have gone through refined renovations. This home includes a two-car garage with additional room for storage as well. Numerous valuable upgrades including the heating and air conditioning system as well as ducting and vents, a water heater with the recirculating system, carpeting, pool pump, and filter system, the entire property was relandscaped, the roof was replaced, and more. The current owners have the utmost pride of ownership and have fine-tuned the design and functionality. Your desert oasis awaits!
